brings his/her own thing to the stage. Pryor has always been my 'favorite',

and Eddie Murphy are the best at miming their bits, but talents like Rock, 
Earthquake, Tosh and Amy Schumer are brilliant with their content. I think 
Chappelle's got a lock on it all. He's got the voice, expressions, mimes, 
poise and delivery. He's able to be angry and nervous and still disarm. On 
top of all this, even though he does the "white folks do this and black 
folks do that" a lot, he has actual content. I hope we get to see more of 
him without him having to freak out too much to deliver it. Not sure what 
"For What It's Worth" cost him 'emotionally', but it sure has shit ranks up 
there with the best standup.﻿

conversation into waters favorable to them. Let me be clear - I am not 
confirming or denying my belief in the Illuminati here. My biggest problem

Illuminate is described as being one of, if not, THE most powerful secret 
organizations in the world in the last several hundred years. So powerful 
and secretive that it has control of the puppet strings of everything - The 
world bank, the military industrial complex, the pharmaceutical mafia and 
even Hollywood and all it's most successful celebrities (perhaps even those 
controlled by Scientology as well as the organization of Scientology 
itself). It is said to be truly omniscient and omnipotent. So much so that 
(and here's where it goes off the rails) nearly EVERYONE with a keyboard 
and an internet connection in the world not only knows about it's existence 
but also can readily identify it's deeds. That, in itself, is an oxymoronic 
condition that, to me, proves it to be a lie. I concede that there may 
actually be a secret cabal of rich, white 1%ers (Tho why we feel the need 
to limit them to rich white men makes no sense to me. This is 2015 - are we 
still trying to pretend that only white males are evil and all the other 
colors of the world are under their boots? Ridiculous IMO. There are evil 
assholes in every color, gender and sexual orientation) out there 
controlling the larger issues of the world. Maybe. But what I am certain of 
is that if that's true - we will never know for sure and we damn sure won't 
know of their name or be able to pinpoint their machinations. Hell even the

Susan, yes I have words.
-
Tomorrow is coming fast.
My world is one of everlasting untold beauty. Marvelous and lovely is the 
world I have prepared for those who truly love and seek ME in this world.
-
MY sheep, this is not your world. You are made for another life, a better 
eternal life. I am coming soon to put you in safe keeping apart from the 
evil of this world.
-
You must wash yourself clean in MY Blood and through MY Word in MY Book.
Surrender and turn your life over to ME.
-
Repent of your sins. I am waiting MY people, MY sheep, the hour is closing 
in.
Very soon, I am coming to get the people. I will bring them out. I have 
planned this for a very long time and the hour is approaching.
I am coming to that point and I will snatch the people out of the grasp of 
MY enemy.
- -
I know who is coming.
- -
You must choose. The choice is yours. I cannot do this choosing for you. I 
am clear about the choices. I have made it very clear. The masses will 
refuse MY offer of escape.
-
They will remain to face an evil that is beyond anything man has witnessed 
or encountered before. I want MY people to avoid the terror coming, but 
they cannot imagine how bad it will be.
The suffering will be immense for the ones who choose against MY enemy.
-
He will punish those who choose against him and the choosing for ME will be 
a difficult one. Now is the time to choose for ME.
Come to ME now and be part of MY bride and I will make you ready to be 
received into MY beautiful Kingdom. If you choose for ME after I remove MY 
bride your choices will be most difficult. The world will go on, but if you 
want to choose for ME you won’t be able to join back into the world.
- -
The alternative will be suffering and death. It will be hard to face. If 
you join in the world system, you will see eternal suffering. Many will 
lose their lives after I come for MY bride.
- -
I am coming for a pure bride.
- -
One who loves ME before anything else—above all others, above all things. I 
am sorry, but these are MY stipulations. I have made this clear in MY Word, 
MY Holy Word. I do not deviate from MY Word.
-
MY Word is clear and uncomplicated.
-
Love ME above all else.
I did not create you to put ME in second or third position in your heart. 
If you believe this, you are mistaken.
You have heard this from someone other than ME. I am a jealous GOD.
-
I do not create MY people to follow after other gods, other lowly, 
worthless gods.
-
If you want to be with ME in MY Holy Home in Heaven, you must count the 
cost in this life. You must evaluate your position and decide for yourself 
what direction you want to move in.
You either come with ME and understand that I, GOD want nothing but first 
place in your heart or choose to put ME in an inferior place in your heart 
and I will allow you to live out the consequences of your choice for 
eternity and without a loving, divine GOD.
-
It will be a bleak eternity. You decide.
You put all your life interests before ME your GOD.
You spend no time communing with your GOD.
I long for relationship with you. I long to share conversations with you, 
to hear your heartfelt words toward ME, your GOD.
- -
I am remote to you. You seek ME when you are in dire circumstances. 
Suddenly you remember MY Name and call out to ME. After your crisis is 
over, I go to the bottom shelf of your heart.
You remember ME not, as if I don’t exist. Why do you suppose I will want 
you in MY eternal home when you have no regard for ME at all? I will spit 
you out. What, this shocks you?
- -
Read MY Word.
- -
Your love for ME is lukewarm and when you come to ME in the next hour, if 
you do not embrace ME now, I will not know you or acknowledge you to MY 
FATHER and HIS Holy Angels.
What has MY sacrifice at Calvary meant to you?
Do you not care what I, GOD did to save you from eternal hell? I, GOD, I, 
JESUS was humbled in a violent way to bring you life eternal and you reject 
MY work on the cross to save you.
-
I do not take this rejection lightly. This is a serious matter.
Your lack of regard for MY sacrifice is belittling of MY Holy Name and MY 
Work on the cross. I endured evil men to save all men, but I will not force 
this salvation. I only make it available to all who want it.
- -
If you do not care for MY sacrifice, MY ransom than you can reject ME, but 
know this…MY FATHER will reject you.
You will stand before MY FATHER and HE will not accept your explanation for 
this sinful way you have led your life and you will receive eternal 
punishment. You will have nothing to say apart from MY sacrifice.
- -
There is no atonement for your evil works. You will be sent to hell for the 
evil you have done against a HOLY GOD.
Accept MY free gift of salvation. Surrender all and repent to your GOD and 
live.
Your time is running out. You have moments left on the clock.
Choose salvation through ME or lose your life to the enemy who is ruthless.
Follow ME,
LORD JESUS

I find this interview very interesting. Amy Schumer, who currently has one 
of the highest rated shows on the Network, was interviewed by Howard Stern 
earlier this year and said that the executives at Comedy Central always 
remind her that she is lucky to have even have a show, and avoid any sort 
of negotiations about a higher salary without taking the money out of the 
production. I think what these two interviews have in common is that art 
and business are very different beasts, and in order for artists to 
continue to achieve and grow, they have to compromise certain aspects of 
their creativity and answer to people who can elevate them or break them 
down. I don't think Dave was wrong in leaving Comedy Central, especially if 
continuing "The Chappelle Show" meant he had to answer to the increasing 
demands of executives, who tend to be more interested in the tastes of 
viewers. They quantify creativity and try to measure the talent of 
creatives with ratings and ad dollars. It's almost sickening. ﻿

I once found a worm in the ground and when I picked it up it was in the

afternoon; I took the Illuminati worm out and put it on my hook. I remember

worm." I casted the hook into the mysteriously unclear water and would you 
believe it, after just 33 seconds there was a fish on my line. I reeled the

got off the hook in the fight. I spent about three hours and 11 minutes on

grabbed the flopping fish and got a better grip. I reposition it back on 
the cutting board and this time held it tight. I pressed the knife down 
against the base of the neck and to my surprise it wiggled itself out 
again. I stared at this disparate fish as it flopped around on my dirty

my rusty clunker and headed back to the place from where I caught the fish.

splashing. I walked towards the end of the dock and knelt down. I tilted 
the bucket towards the dark murky water as I slowly poured out the freedom 
of a small fish.
